Click on the 'More Info' button below for details or to turn off automatic logs."

"T-Mobile Issue Assist monitors for the following events:
\u0009Call Drop \u0009Call Fail \u0009Data Session Fail \u0009Data Session Drop \u0009Enter No Coverage \u0009Enter Roaming
When an event from the above list is detected, T-Mobile will receive location information and the issue description, along with some identifiable information in order to help us follow up with a resolution.
Additionally, Issue Assist periodically schedules automated diagnostic tests for your network connection, such as download & upload speeds as well as your signal strength, which T-Mobile will receive along with location information in order to assist with improving your network experience.
You will NOT be charged for data usage from Issue Assist reports."
